Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.07,0:00:11.78,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}sore wa sore wa chiisai te de aozora wo aoida
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.09,0:00:18.41,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}sanagara mukashi kara yoku shiru tonari no ano ko no you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.14,0:00:23.27,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}katahou no mimitabu de kiku sotsugyou no canon
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:29.23,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}hitori demo daijoubu yo tte mekureteru watashi no story
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:31.51,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}dareka no sei ni shitai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.51,0:00:35.55,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}tsurai naa iya iya
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.55,0:00:41.05,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}kanashikutte naite bakkari itara me ga tokete nakunatta
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.67,0:00:46.47,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}aki ni nari mata fuyu ni nari hitotsu toshi wo totta
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.10,0:00:53.26,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}tooku made nigete iru tsumori demo owaranai kimi no story
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.26,0:00:55.52,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}niya niya waratte iru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.52,0:00:59.11,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}fugainaiya iya
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.11,0:01:05.25,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}sugari nagara oikakete mitemo ashige ni saretemo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:07.44,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}aita ana wo fusagou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.44,0:01:10.36,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}chigai nai ya iya
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.36,0:01:17.74,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}fugainai ya iya
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.33,0:01:28.36,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}tsurai naa iya iya
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.18,0:00:06.24,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}My hometown lay buried in snow the morning I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.07,0:00:11.78,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I looked up at the blue sky with my tiny hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.09,0:00:18.41,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}The face of the girl next door that I've known so well...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.14,0:00:23.27,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's as familiar as the graduation canon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:29.23,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Thriving in solitude has been mistaken as my life story.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:31.51,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I want to blame it on someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.51,0:00:35.55,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so difficult. No, I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.55,0:00:41.05,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Tears and sorrow caused me to miss my chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.67,0:00:46.47,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Autumn passed, winter came again, and I became a year older.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.10,0:00:53.26,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}You think you've run far away, but your story never ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.26,0:00:55.52,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}And yet, you're smirking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.52,0:00:59.11,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so cowardly. I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.11,0:01:05.25,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Even if I have to cling to you, chase after you, and get kicked down...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:07.44,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}...I'll close the hole that's opened...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.44,0:01:10.36,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}...without a doubt. No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.36,0:01:17.74,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so cowardly. No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.33,0:01:28.36,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so difficult. I hate it. I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.19,0:01:42.73,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Kaoru disappeared on the day the year's first snow fell on the gray city.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.03,0:01:50.09,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I should've realized somewhere along the line...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.37,0:01:55.45,thoughts,,0,0,0,,But... I just couldn't change the flow of events...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.33,0:02:03.22,clover,,0,0,0,,Let's go somewhere warm for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.81,0:02:07.92,clover,,0,0,0,,Let's eat some good food, stare out at the ocean, and relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.58,0:02:12.70,clover,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:17.21,clover,,0,0,0,,I can tell... you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.06,0:02:21.75,clover,,0,0,0,,You look like you're thinking, "Ah, I'm finally free of my responsibilities."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.32,0:02:24.18,clover,,0,0,0,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.78,0:02:28.41,clover,,0,0,0,,You tagged along with me because you had to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.85,0:02:30.70,clover,,0,0,0,,Even though you disobeyed Dad's instructions...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:36.01,clover,,0,0,0,,Dad said it, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.09,0:02:38.73,clover,,0,0,0,,To head towards the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.13,0:02:43.32,clover,,0,0,0,,You could see it, couldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.40,0:02:47.60,clover,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't see the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.25,0:02:50.08,clover,,0,0,0,,I couldn't even tell where it was coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.78,0:02:51.83,clover,,0,0,0,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:56.67,clover,,0,0,0,,There's no point in being told by someone talented like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.70,0:02:59.36,clover,,0,0,0,,I don't have anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.88,0:03:04.03,clover,,0,0,0,,Dad only cared about you until the very end...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:09.49,clover,,0,0,0,,I wonder what it would've been like, to be like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.24,0:03:19.61,clover,,0,0,0,,Shiroyama-san, I... Was I mistaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.99,0:03:25.58,clover,,0,0,0,,Exacting revenge isn't suited for someone with imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.32,0:03:29.78,clover,,0,0,0,,Besides, Kaoru-sama is kind to a fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.42,0:03:33.88,clover,,0,0,0,,He receives back all the damage he gives.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.68,0:03:37.82,clover,,0,0,0,,If something were to happen to Kaoru, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.42,0:03:39.63,clover,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.09,0:03:41.40,clover,,0,0,0,,Didn't I just say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.84,0:03:43.92,clover,,0,0,0,,Kaoru-sama has a gifted imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:50.85,clover,,0,0,0,,On top of that, he's very smart and has an annoyingly sharp memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.59,0:03:50.85,note,,0,0,0,,Like I said, when we ate natto together at Shiroyama's parents' house!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.32,0:03:54.81,clover,,0,0,0,,The combinations of Matsuda-san's efforts all these years in Chicago...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.14,0:04:00.86,clover,,0,0,0,,All the effort we put forth for the past twenty years...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.54,0:04:06.24,clover,,0,0,0,,And above all, the image of you, who loved and stayed with him for all these years...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.24,0:04:15.11,clover,,0,0,0,,...must be filling his head and preventing him from harming himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.39,0:04:25.05,clover,,0,0,0,,Sorry, can you leave her alone for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.60,0:04:27.88,clover,,0,0,0,,Is she not feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:30.39,clover,,0,0,0,,Well, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:36.20,clover,,0,0,0,,Hagu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:39.54,clover,,0,0,0,,Hagu, does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.99,0:04:41.17,clover,,0,0,0,,Do you want to take some painkillers?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.41,0:04:43.99,clover,,0,0,0,,It's okay, I can handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.65,0:04:46.86,clover,,0,0,0,,If I take them, I won't be able to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.33,0:04:55.20,clover,,0,0,0,,If the pain doesn't come back to my hand, it means that my nerves haven't reconnected, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.63,0:05:00.29,clover,,0,0,0,,In that case, I need to go back to surgery as soon as possible, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.37,0:05:03.10,clover,,0,0,0,,That's why, for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.72,0:05:08.70,clover,,0,0,0,,Hagu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.15,0:05:11.54,clover,,0,0,0,,S-Shuu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.57,0:05:14.00,clover,,0,0,0,,S-Shuu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.40,0:05:17.27,clover,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Hagu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:21.23,clover,,0,0,0,,It's back...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:23.69,clover,,0,0,0,,The pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.48,0:05:25.69,clover,,0,0,0,,It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.42,0:05:29.20,clover,,0,0,0,,My hand... it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.28,0:05:31.75,clover,,0,0,0,,It's connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.40,0:05:33.85,clover,,0,0,0,,My hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:37.41,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.88,0:05:39.71,clover,,0,0,0,,Hagu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:41.11,clover,,0,0,0,,Hagu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:48.97,clover,,0,0,0,,So, she hasn't slept at all since then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:53.65,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I've told Hagu everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.65,0:05:56.68,clover,,0,0,0,,I also had the doctor give her an overview.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:06:00.23,clover,,0,0,0,,If the nerves don't reconnect...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.23,0:06:02.65,clover,,0,0,0,,...a second surgery would be performed as soon as possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.18,0:06:06.13,clover,,0,0,0,,...since neurology is a race against time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:09.25,clover,,0,0,0,,That's why Hagu was desperately searching...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.86,0:06:12.15,clover,,0,0,0,,...amidst all the pain from her other wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:15.07,clover,,0,0,0,,Just to feel the sensation from her right hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:18.83,clover,,0,0,0,,She rejected all painkillers and stabilizers...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.23,0:06:20.58,clover,,0,0,0,,She even refused to sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.78,0:06:24.87,clover,,0,0,0,,All so she can keep searching in the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:32.26,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Hagu-chan is amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.51,0:06:34.76,thoughts,,0,0,0,,To be honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:41.23,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Both Yamada-san and I were overwhelmed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:44.70,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...by her inner strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.64,0:06:50.25,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...and by her strong will that's capable of repressing the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.82,0:06:55.49,clover,,0,0,0,,From this point on is the crucial stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.49,0:06:58.47,clover,,0,0,0,,Everything after this will depend on her rehabilitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.05,0:07:03.54,clover,,0,0,0,,Knowing Hagu, she'll never give up until she regains movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.87,0:07:09.13,clover,,0,0,0,,There are apparently cases where rehab won't bring back sensation to your fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.41,0:07:13.81,clover,,0,0,0,,Whether she'll be able to draw with a brush like before...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.75,0:07:20.14,clover,,0,0,0,,She might have to live with numbness and other sensory disabilities for the rest of her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:24.38,clover,,0,0,0,,Her efforts alone may not be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:29.59,clover,,0,0,0,,But if she doesn't try, she'll lose it all for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.90,0:07:38.43,thoughts,,0,0,0,,God, please save her...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.88,0:07:46.95,clover,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.95,0:07:49.78,clover,,0,0,0,,You're finally getting a cellphone, Yamada-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.85,0:07:52.36,clover,,0,0,0,,Nomiya-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.56,0:07:55.69,clover,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.69,0:07:57.30,clover,,0,0,0,,So you were looking at cellphones...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.86,0:08:00.28,clover,,0,0,0,,I want to be able to help out in any way possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.81,0:08:03.50,clover,,0,0,0,,...so I thought it would be better if I had one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:06.48,clover,,0,0,0,,But I honestly don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.99,0:08:13.34,clover,,0,0,0,,Is there really anything someone like me could do for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.49,0:08:20.45,clover,,0,0,0,,This might sound cliche, but I truly realized that we live in different worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.58,0:08:24.33,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.75,0:08:27.99,clover,,0,0,0,,Everyone probably thinks that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:32.04,clover,,0,0,0,,And everyone will distance themselves from her...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.66,0:08:36.10,clover,,0,0,0,,All saying, "There probably isn't anything I can do for her."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:40.22,clover,,0,0,0,,And before you know it, she's all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.94,0:08:45.25,clover,,0,0,0,,She's probably stressed out right now on whether or not her hand will move again...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:49.45,clover,,0,0,0,,...but she'll probably suffer the most during the rehab that's coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.45,0:08:53.48,clover,,0,0,0,,Yamada-san, you should stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.85,0:08:54.86,clover,,0,0,0,,You need to stay with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:08:58.01,clover,,0,0,0,,You're her friend, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.89,0:09:03.68,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:08.12,clover,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Nomiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:12.50,clover,,0,0,0,,Sheesh... what a troublesome girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.17,0:09:17.92,clover,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh, crap, they heard me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.59,0:09:18.46,clover,,0,0,0,,U-Um... well..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:19.81,clover,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I was saying something childish like "You're her friend, aren't you?"...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.34,0:09:22.42,clover,,0,0,0,,What I meant was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.81,0:09:21.66,clover,,0,0,0,,{\an8}...even though I'm already over thirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:23.68,clover,,0,0,0,,{\an8}They'll never let me live this down as long as I live...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.68,0:09:25.23,clover,,0,0,0,,{\an8}...like, what am I gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.23,0:09:28.01,clover,,0,0,0,,Nomiya, good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.93,0:09:31.44,dog,,0,0,0,,{\t(0,2072,\fscx65.26\fscy77.78)\move(376,353,313,373,0,2072)\fad(0,396)}Ah, Miwako-san. Please don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.45,0:09:31.98,clover,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:39.90,clover,,0,0,0,,Friends, huh? It gets me every time... Just hearing it brings tears to my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:46.01,clover,,0,0,0,,I can sympathize. When you're our age, a lot of things become more complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.01,0:09:48.70,clover,,0,0,0,,All your friends start to become estranged...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.70,0:09:51.50,clover,,0,0,0,,That's not true! I'm here for you, Yamazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.78,0:09:53.75,clover,,0,0,0,,M-Miwako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.75,0:09:56.50,clover,,0,0,0,,We'll be friends forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.08,0:09:56.50,sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,0)\fax-0.1\bord4\be2\fs64\frz59.811\pos(442,140)\c&HA56A5B&\3c&H505956&}It's all right
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.50,0:09:59.50,clover,,0,0,0,,Friends forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.74,0:10:01.47,dog,,0,0,0,,{\an1\frz278.967\move(150,487,78,52,28,1779)}Oh no, Yamazaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.47,0:10:06.37,clover,,0,0,0,,We're going to prove that there are friendships that stand the test of adulthood!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:08.63,dog,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,375)\fad(401,145)}Oh, this is fun stuff! Ruff!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.39,0:10:11.50,clover,,0,0,0,,S-S-Sis, please stop already...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.93,0:10:11.50,clover,,0,0,0,,Friends! Friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.83,0:10:19.36,clover,,0,0,0,,I'd always felt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.02,0:10:24.72,clover,,0,0,0,,Even though she'd be in front of me, it felt like she was looking into a different world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.07,0:10:31.63,clover,,0,0,0,,She's here now, but someday she'll float far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.24,0:10:33.90,clover,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.58,0:10:37.16,thoughts,,0,0,0,,You're her friend, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.00,0:10:44.70,clover,,0,0,0,,Hagu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:47.66,clover,,0,0,0,,Ayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.30,0:10:57.56,clover,,0,0,0,,How is it? It's a little too lumpy, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.81,0:11:00.99,clover,,0,0,0,,It's warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:05.76,clover,,0,0,0,,It's so that your back and shoulders won't get cold when you sit up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:07.45,clover,,0,0,0,,It's got down in it, so it's light, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:10.38,clover,,0,0,0,,Let's make you a better pillow to rest your arm on, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.38,0:11:12.41,clover,,0,0,0,,You could use a cuter one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.41,0:11:15.17,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, and I brought some grapes as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.17,0:11:18.34,clover,,0,0,0,,The Red Grove, the non-peel kind that you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.34,0:11:21.87,clover,,0,0,0,,Um, there's that, books, and MDs...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.87,0:11:24.34,clover,,0,0,0,,Ayu, you have a feather in your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.84,0:11:26.05,clover,,0,0,0,,On your sweater, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:29.68,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, man! I thought I got them all before I left home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.39,0:11:34.64,clover,,0,0,0,,Actually, I made that cape using my Dad's old down jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.64,0:11:37.44,clover,,0,0,0,,The room got filled with feathers, it was such a mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.44,0:11:41.11,clover,,0,0,0,,I just cut right into it with scissors, and the down all came flying out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.33,0:11:45.24,clover,,0,0,0,,It was so bad, it took me two hours to clean up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.66,0:11:49.07,clover,,0,0,0,,Ayu, there's a bunch more on your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.07,0:11:52.02,clover,,0,0,0,,Aw... man, no way! Can you get them off?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:54.57,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:11:57.58,thoughts,,0,0,0,,You don't need to get them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.54,0:11:59.71,clover,,0,0,0,,Hagu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.59,0:12:02.46,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.53,0:12:06.18,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I mean, you look just like an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.05,0:12:11.47,clover,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:14.45,clover,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Ayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:24.77,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll come again at 2 P.M. tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.59,0:12:27.86,clover,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, Dr. Satsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.33,0:12:31.03,clover,,0,0,0,,The shock seems to have been a little too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.90,0:12:32.66,clover,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.76,0:12:52.66,clover,,0,0,0,,Hanamoto-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.13,0:12:54.06,clover,,0,0,0,,Hanamoto-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.89,0:12:57.54,clover,,0,0,0,,Are you listening, Hanamoto-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:12:59.52,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.52,0:13:03.23,clover,,0,0,0,,Hagumi-san's upper body is getting stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:09.78,clover,,0,0,0,,Like I mentioned yesterday, please massage her shoulders and upper arm, taking care to avoid her wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.27,0:13:12.81,clover,,0,0,0,,All you have to do is gently give her a rub.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.15,0:13:15.66,clover,,0,0,0,,The aim here is to get her to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.20,0:13:19.37,clover,,0,0,0,,Let's take things steadily and optimistically.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.37,0:13:19.87,clover,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:22.24,clover,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.71,0:13:31.09,clover,,0,0,0,,E-Expensive...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.65,0:13:33.98,clover,,0,0,0,,Flowers sure are expensive...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:36.38,clover,,0,0,0,,This little thing is 300 yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.38,0:13:38.57,clover,,0,0,0,,If 1,000 yen will only get me three...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.57,0:13:41.59,clover,,0,0,0,,...how much would it cost me to get a bouquet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.59,0:13:43.23,clover,,0,0,0,,Takemoto-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.54,0:13:45.38,clover,,0,0,0,,Y-Yamada-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.71,0:13:46.84,clover,,0,0,0,,For Hagu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:50.22,clover,,0,0,0,,Ah, well, I thought flowers might be nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:51.23,clover,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.23,0:13:52.11,clover,,0,0,0,,Takemoto-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.52,0:13:54.87,clover,,0,0,0,,Wanna go somewhere nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.95,0:14:02.50,clover,,0,0,0,,Yamada-san, is this that "somewhere nice"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.58,0:14:04.92,clover,,0,0,0,,Yep, this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.63,0:14:08.13,clover,,0,0,0,,There are plenty of flowers here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:09.60,clover,,0,0,0,,You can pick all you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.60,0:14:11.53,clover,,0,0,0,,We'll tell her that we picked them ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:13.82,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she'll be happier that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.96,0:14:16.27,clover,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.09,0:14:21.46,clover,,0,0,0,,Here you go, Hagu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.48,0:14:25.92,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.93,0:14:28.24,clover,,0,0,0,,They're freshly picked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.24,0:14:30.32,clover,,0,0,0,,We got them on the embankment by the train tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.32,0:14:36.62,clover,,0,0,0,,The stonecrop was actually the biggest and cutest, but it had too much pollen, so we skipped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.50,0:14:44.84,clover,,0,0,0,,Hagu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.21,0:14:52.09,clover,,0,0,0,,No way... She doesn't have any sensation...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.64,0:14:56.05,clover,,0,0,0,,In her fingertips? Can such a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.35,0:14:59.16,clover,,0,0,0,,Her rehab has just began.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.64,0:15:06.26,clover,,0,0,0,,Plus, I hear that there are many who started where Hagu is and ultimately regained the sensation in their fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.26,0:15:07.24,clover,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.19,0:15:13.75,clover,,0,0,0,,Yamada-san, there's no rushing or giving up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:15.91,clover,,0,0,0,,That applies to the three of us as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.46,0:15:21.85,clover,,0,0,0,,If the people watching over start to waver, the person who's drowning won't have anyone to grab onto.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:28.67,clover,,0,0,0,,So with that said, let's all set our own bases...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.21,0:15:31.03,clover,,0,0,0,,Aren't you supposed to man the store on Wednesdays?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:33.63,clover,,0,0,0,,And Takemoto! Get cracking on your senior thesis!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.22,0:15:37.26,clover,,0,0,0,,Haven't you two been coming every day lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.26,0:15:40.89,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm thankful, but you can't neglect your personal lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.16,0:15:43.19,clover,,0,0,0,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:45.31,clover,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.31,0:15:48.87,clover,,0,0,0,,The person who was here last night... Was that Hagu-chan's father?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:02.41,clover,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:07.61,clover,,0,0,0,,I could tell from what I saw last night and Sensei's expression just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:09.38,clover,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:14.69,clover,,0,0,0,,That the place she was supposed to be able to return to isn't the same anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.75,0:16:17.09,clover,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.09,0:16:18.36,clover,,0,0,0,,It's not anyone's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.71,0:16:21.73,clover,,0,0,0,,We're all just trying our best to live our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:26.21,clover,,0,0,0,,But God, why must all of this happen at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.13,0:16:30.99,clover,,0,0,0,,At this rate, she won't be able to take much more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.61,0:16:33.70,clover,,0,0,0,,She...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:43.45,clover,,0,0,0,,Bruises that looked like red flowers started appearing on Hagu-chan's left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.48,0:16:49.08,clover,,0,0,0,,The stress is causing her to bite herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.70,0:16:54.07,clover,,0,0,0,,But after a while, those bruises moved to Sensei's wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:16:59.26,thoughts,,0,0,0,,The person who's drowning won't have anyone to grab onto.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.22,0:17:02.75,clover,,0,0,0,,Sensei was so composed, it was scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.41,0:17:07.23,clover,,0,0,0,,For Hagu-chan's sake, he must've sworn not to waver no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.60,0:17:11.23,clover,,0,0,0,,I got a fax from Shin-san yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.23,0:17:14.23,note,,0,0,0,,To Takemoto-kun: Greetings, we're now working in Morioka. Regarding your job, we'd like for you to join us around mid-April.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:17.83,clover,,0,0,0,,Their new work is in Morioka, and they'd like me to join them by mid-April.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:22.91,clover,,0,0,0,,The day for us to part is drawing ever closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:26.19,clover,,0,0,0,,Are we really just going to drift apart?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.86,0:17:29.94,clover,,0,0,0,,Am I going to leave her while she's like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.45,0:17:32.40,clover,,0,0,0,,I should forget about Morioka and stay in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.42,0:17:35.96,clover,,0,0,0,,Or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.96,0:17:37.58,clover,,0,0,0,,What am I thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.58,0:17:40.34,clover,,0,0,0,,What am I going to do if I don't take this job?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.64,0:17:43.87,clover,,0,0,0,,What is a life for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:50.52,clover,,0,0,0,,Isn't it so you can be there to tightly grip the hand of someone close to you at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.39,0:17:53.69,clover,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.69,0:17:55.16,clover,,0,0,0,,I should quit and stay by her side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.53,0:17:57.99,clover,,0,0,0,,I can encourage her through rehab.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.53,0:18:02.52,clover,,0,0,0,,To make time to care for her, I can just choose a part-time job that allows me a flexible schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.14,0:18:07.91,clover,,0,0,0,,Like a janitor, road construction worker, or late-night convenience stock clerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,0:18:11.12,clover,,0,0,0,,But wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.31,0:18:16.35,clover,,0,0,0,,Could I live alone in Tokyo on an income like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.72,0:18:20.70,clover,,0,0,0,,Right now, I'm living off of money sent from home and my part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.49,0:18:27.99,clover,,0,0,0,,It's obvious, but I'll have to become independent once I graduate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:33.26,clover,,0,0,0,,No, I'll be all right if I work as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.26,0:18:35.39,clover,,0,0,0,,I can make a living if I'm not wasteful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.01,0:18:42.37,clover,,0,0,0,,But... if I work that much, I won't have the time to care for Hagu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.33,0:18:48.43,clover,,0,0,0,,And in the first place, what am I going to do once she gets better?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.03,0:18:55.59,clover,,0,0,0,,What if, after my family helped put me through this expensive art school...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.80,0:19:02.88,clover,,0,0,0,,...I fail to find a proper job, I don't have a steady job, and I'm already past thirty?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.44,0:19:09.06,clover,,0,0,0,,If that were to happen, wouldn't my very existence be a burden to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.51,0:19:17.33,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}hajime kara sono tsumori de kimi wa ita no kamo nante\NYou never were in love with me to begin with, I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.99,0:19:15.06,clover,,0,0,0,,I though back to Mayama-san's words...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:18.70,thoughts,,0,0,0,,If something were to happen to the woman I love...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.30,0:19:24.08,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}sore nara sore de betsu ni ii ya\NI don't really care when I think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.70,0:19:25.49,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...I want to have enough to be able to tell her, "Go ahead and take some time off."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.49,0:19:31.87,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}ima sara tashikame you mo nai\NIt's not like I can go back and check.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:29.70,clover,,0,0,0,,I've just now become truly aware of the meaning behind those words.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.31,0:19:37.08,clover,,0,0,0,,A man who can't even buy a tiny flower like that can't possibly save a girl whom he loves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.32,0:19:37.08,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}dare wo nikundara ii\NWho am I supposed to hate?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.21,0:19:40.49,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm making excuses to substitute for the real problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.87,0:19:43.42,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}nani wo oshikoroseba ii\NWhat emotions am I supposed to hold back?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.16,0:19:47.08,clover,,0,0,0,,I say that I want to save her, but in reality, I just don't want to be apart from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:58.01,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}te wo furazu ni satte iku hou wa boku yori kanashii no kanaa\NWas the person who left without a goodbye the sadder of the two?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.40,0:20:09.41,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}nee ima boku no mune wa haritsumete shimau bakari de\NHey, all my heart can do now is hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.37,0:20:22.41,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}tada namida dake ga darashi naku ochiru no desu\NI'm just crying here pathetically.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.67,0:20:35.73,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}kanashimi wa nami no you ni nando mo kurikaesurashii\NI hear sorrow repeats over and over like the waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.62,0:20:50.82,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}warui tsume wo hagu toki mitai ni itsuka yukkuri hagarete iku no kanaa\NI wonder if it'll grow out on its own like a damaged fingernail?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.61,0:21:29.75,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}arifurete iru kimochi nante sa
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.61,0:21:29.75,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}It would be so much easier...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.11,0:21:40.21,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}nanimo iwazu ni isso kieteshimaeba
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.11,0:21:40.21,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}...if these stale emotions...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.21,0:21:43.63,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,raku ni nareru no ni
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.21,0:21:43.63,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,...could just disappear without a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.63,0:21:52.76,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}sorezore no michi wo yuku sono wakaremichi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.63,0:21:52.76,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}At the crossroads where we split ways...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.31,0:22:06.24,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}mou nidoto au koto no nai deai wa kanashisugiru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.31,0:22:06.24,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}...it saddens me to think we may never meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.24,0:22:08.98,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,tarinai kimochi wo mochiyotte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.24,0:22:08.98,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,Despite adding the emotions that are lacking...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.98,0:22:11.84,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,atatameta saki kara hieteitte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.98,0:22:11.84,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,...things cool off just as soon as I warm them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.84,0:22:16.18,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}sonna hazu naitte shinjiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.84,0:22:16.18,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}...but I still don't want to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.55,0:22:24.88,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}ittai itsumade onaji kotoba wo kakaekondenda
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.55,0:22:24.88,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}Just how long am I going to brood over the same word?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.88,0:22:28.28,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}kakekondenda
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.88,0:22:28.28,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}How long...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.49,0:22:34.95,clover,,0,0,0,,Next episode: Once, when I was little, I saw God.
